    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Eight Mile Plains?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Eight Mile Plains values are driven by proximity to the business park and tech precinct, the Pacific Motorway and Logan Motorway interchange, and strong rental demand from professionals employed in the nearby employment centres. The school catchments add appeal for owner-occupiers with families. Properties that present well and sit in a good position relative to the employment corridor consistently attract both owner-occupier and investor interest, and the depth of the buyer pool reflects the suburb's dual appeal.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Eight Mile Plains?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Eight Mile Plains homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The suburb's dual owner-occupier and investor buyer pool means that genuine buyer interest is consistent across the year. Buyers in this market tend to make practical decisions efficiently when a property is correctly priced and well presented. Correct pricing against recent comparable sales is the most controllable factor in determining campaign length.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Eight Mile Plains?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Eight Mile Plains offers a well-connected, practical lifestyle about fifteen kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD. The suburb's motorway access, proximity to Garden City in Upper Mount Gravatt, and its well-maintained residential streets make it an efficient place to live for professionals who commute across Brisbane. Local parks and reserves provide everyday outdoor space, and the surrounding southern corridor offers a full range of day-to-day amenity.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Eight Mile Plains a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Eight Mile Plains offers genuine appeal for owner-occupiers and investors who understand the southern Brisbane employment corridor. The suburb's motorway access, proximity to major employers, strong rental demand, and competitive price point relative to closer-in southern suburbs make it a practical long-term property holding. Its depth of buyer and tenant demand reflects the suburb's real employment and commuter fundamentals.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

